    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just \"fleeting\" though. it's gone. when you're at the top, you're someone. people respect you, they listen to you. now, i walk into a room and i can see people looking right through me like i'm not even there. it's like the person i was actually died. how am i supposed to just \"be\" when there's no one left to be for?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
